
@host = http://localhost:8080/r4


### CDA ClinicalDocument TO FHIR Bundle
### Note: Post the maps in the following order, if you update the map you need to repost also the maps below


### 1. POST CdaToFhirTypes.map

POST {{host}}/StructureMap HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/fhir+xml;fhirVersion=4.0
Content-Type: text/fhir-mapping

< ./input/maps/CdaToFhirTypes.map


### POST CdaToBundle
POST {{host}}/StructureMap HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/fhir+xml;fhirVersion=4.0
Content-Type: text/fhir-mapping

< ./input/maps/CdaToBundle.map

### POST CdaChToBundle
POST {{host}}/StructureMap HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/fhir+xml;fhirVersion=4.0
Content-Type: text/fhir-mapping

< ./input/maps/CdaChToBundle.map

### POST CdaChEmedMedicationCardDocumentToBundle.map 
POST {{host}}/StructureMap HTTP/1.1
